data.description: Lovingly maintained home on over half an acre with open floor plan situated on the large lake with water view.  Wood floors in all living areas.  Ceramic tile floors in bathrooms and carpet in bedrooms. Kitchen features corian counter tops, all appliances and upgraded cabinets.  Breakfast room too.  Kitchen is open to the spacious great room - fireplace is electric and can stay with the home. Formal dining room. Master suite features walk-in closet and his and her vanities. Fenced rear. Large half acre lot. Shed. Sprinkler system. Has a deep well with airiator and septic tank.  Lots of room for all your toys! Note: Formal LR is being used as an office. Can also be a 4th bedroom.
